{"id":551487433,"lang":"cpp","time":"4 days, 16 hours","timestamp":1631106991,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"20 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/551487433/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"8.3 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int lengthOfLongestSubstring(string s) {\n        unordered_map<char,int>freq;\n        int i=0,j=0,len=0;\n        while(i<s.length())\n        {\n            while(j<s.length() and freq[s[j]]==0)\n            {\n                freq[s[j]]++;\n                j++;\n            }\n            len=max(j-i,len);\n            freq[s[i]]--;\n            i++;\n        }\n        return len;\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters"}
